    <descript>
      <abstract>Data available online through the Arkansas Spatial Data Infrastructure (ASDI) at http://gis.arkansas.gov. The feature dataset contain points for Newspaper publishing cities in the State of Arkansas. The compilation of this dataset was done using resources available on the publications website and contact data collected by the Arkansas Department of Health (ADH). The project was a collaborative effort between the Arkansas Geographic Information Systems Office and ADH to build a comprehensive geographic database of Media (TV, Radio, Newspapers) coverage's in the state for external communication purposes.</abstract>
      <purpose>The feature dataset serves as an essential tool for the state Department of Health to determine coverage-based information about the media outlet. This critical information is useful to alert the media in case of an emergency and notify the public of a possible disease outbreak, or a bio-terrorism threat. The database provides location information for use in local and regional spatial analysis applications.</purpose>
    </descript>
